@layer base {
  * {
    @apply border-border;
  }
  body {
    @apply bg-background text-foreground;
  }
}

/* Animation for breathing exercise */
@keyframes expand {
  from {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
  to {
    transform: scale(1.2);
  }
}

@keyframes contract {
  from {
    transform: scale(1.2);
  }
  to {
    transform: scale(1);
  }
}

.animate-expand {
  animation: expand 4s ease-in-out;
}

.animate-hold {
  animation: none;
}

.animate-contract {
  animation: contract 6s ease-in-out;
}
